# Processed data directory

This directory contains processed and structured data ready for analysis or export.

## Structure
- `csv/` - CSV files with extracted product data
- `json/` - Processed JSON files with cleaned data
- `parquet/` - Apache Parquet files for big data processing
- `exports/` - Exported data in various formats

## File Naming Convention
- `{platform}_{date}_{timestamp}.csv`
- `{platform}_{date}_{timestamp}.json`
- `{platform}_{date}_{timestamp}.parquet`

## Usage
Files in this directory are generated by the data processing pipeline.
These files are safe to use for analysis and reporting.

## Data Schema
Each processed file contains the following columns:
- id: Unique identifier
- title: Product title
- price: Product price
- currency: Currency code
- platform: Source platform
- url: Product URL
- scraped_at: Timestamp of scraping
- ... additional platform-specific fields
